  "title": "How to reconcile your premium tax credit",
  "meta-title": "How to reconcile your premium tax credit",
  "meta-description": "You must reconcile your premium tax credit when you file your tax return if you were enrolled in Health Insurance Marketplace\u00ae plan.",
  "title-short": null,
  "bite": "If you had a Marketplace plan and used premium tax credits, you\u2019ll have to reconcile when you file your federal taxes.",
